## Quick Reference

**Key Directories:**
- `src/` - Core implementation code (Python modules)
- `notebooks/` - Jupyter notebooks for interactive learning
- `docs/` - Study notes and planning documentation
  - `docs/reviews/` - **All review reports MUST go here**
  - `docs/reference/` - Reference materials (git, PowerShell, Python commands)
- `tests/` - Unit tests (to be created)

**Key Entry Points:**
- `src/main.py` - Main entry point
- `notebooks/ch02/01_ch02.ipynb` - Chapter 2 learning notebook
- `pyproject.toml` - Project dependencies (uv)

**Planned Structure** (as project grows):
- `src/tokenization/` - Tokenizer implementations
- `src/model/` - GPT/Transformer architecture
- `src/training/` - Training loops and optimization
- `src/evaluation/` - Metrics and analysis

